{"tid":1284961,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］白色恐佈 醫護狗入","createTime":"2019-07-04T11:25:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T13:52:46.000Z","uid":274059,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1de723fb7670b29260ea042a79226da558606893","tid":1284961,"uid":274059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:25:33.000Z","msg":"發夢我同我個fd都係護士<br />\n頭先我收到廣華急症室打黎既電話話搵xxx<br />\n我答左我唔係個條友 <br />\n咁啱我個fd個名係類似既中文譯音<br />\n我就問番佢搵我個fd做咩同埋佢搵既人係男定女 <br />\n打黎條友答唔到係男定女 係度答非所問 不斷重複咁問你識唔識個個人先 仲話留電話比我叫我個fd call back番佢 <br />\n我求其比左個fd聽 話佢係我隔離<br />\n打黎條友問我個fd係咪有睇過廣華急症室 <br />\n我個fd話無之後佢仲double confirm多次之後就收左線<br />\n<br />\n利申： 我fd發夢出過去金鐘行街 但非勇武"},{"pid":"54c70845f503e540ec39747fd0f1a4441cd02c28","tid":1284961,"uid":199827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:26:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6e4b4ac1984e0af1bc0b68a3e5dd2885b6a5c1f9","tid":1284961,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:27:29.000Z","msg":"WTF<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac86a1853d15c67168c8443d55a53941a7a21e32","tid":1284961,"uid":30273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:31:29.000Z","msg":"一定要push<br />\n<br />\n 我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"6cf38039ff42772a08312372379c5000d94c1a71","tid":1284961,"uid":30273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:31:45.000Z","msg":"Push 多下"},{"pid":"dacf30b4bcc21451f6228a6594f908fbe7327bf9","tid":1284961,"uid":59886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:31:59.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"a8fe4aae8a7d658d3c627f16bfb6074a007ceeb9","tid":1284961,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:33:41.000Z","msg":"前幾日都好似有呢啲post講有唔識既人打比佢<br />\n又係乜都答唔出<br />\n有冇巴絲搵得番"},{"pid":"3f9f30db7dac97b9df19642ff524cf5d8faa2f84","tid":1284961,"uid":44277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:33:45.0